quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Dumisa igama leNkosi yakho ephakeme kakhulu
  87,2,Okuyiyona eyadala yalinganisa (konke ngesimo sako)
  87,3,Futhi okuyiyona ekalayo futhi eholayo
  87,4,Futhi okuyiyona eyaveza okuluhlaza (utshani nezihlahla)
  87,5,Yabe seyikwenza kwaba yizinhlanga ezinsundu
  87,6,Sizokwenza ukuthi ufunde angeke ukhohlwe
  87,7,"Ngaphandle kwalokho okufiswa nguMvelinqangi, ngempela yena uyakwazi okusobala kanye nalokho okufihlekile"
  87,8,Futhi sikwenzela kubelula okulula
  87,9,"Ngakho-ke\tkhumbuza\tuma\tkungukuthi\tsiyakusiza isikhumbuzo"
  87,10,Uyokhumbula lowo owesaba (uMvelinqangi)
  87,11,Futhi uyokugwema (ukukhunjuzwa) lowo muntu omubi kakhulu
  87,12,Lowo uzokusha emlilweni omkhulu
  87,13,Bese engafi lapho phakathi kuwona futhi angaphili
  87,14,Ngempela uphumelele lowo ozihlanzayo
  87,15,Futhi akhumbule igama leNkosi yakhe athandaze
  87,16,Kepha nikhetha impilo yalomhlaba
  87,17,Futhi impilo ezayo ingcono futhi ingehlalayo engapheliyo
  87,18,Ngempela lokhu kusemibhalweni yokuqala
  87,19,Imibhalo ka-Abrahamu noMose
  88,1,Ngakube seyafika yini kuwena indaba yesehlakalo esehlulayo
  88,2,Ubuso ngalolosuku buyothotshiswa
  88,3,Busebenza bukhandlekile
  88,4,Bungena emlilweni ovuthayo
  88,5,Buphuziswa esiphethwini esibilayo
  88,6,"Abanako\tukudla\tngaphandle\tkwesihlahla\tsameva sasesihogweni"
  88,7,Isihlahla asondli futhi asisizi ekulweni nendlala
  88,8,(Obunye) ubuso ngalolosuku buyothokoza
  88,9,Buthokozela imizamo yabo
  88,10,Esivandeni esiphakeme
  88,11,Awuyizwa lapho phakathi inkulumo eyilize (engamanga)
  88,12,Lapho phakathi kunomthombo ogelezayo
  88,13,Lapho phakathi kunemibhede ephakanyisiwe
  88,14,Nezinkomishi ezibekiwe
  88,15,Nemiqamelo ebekwe yaba uhlu
  88,16,Kanye nabokhaphethi abendlaliwe
  88,17,Ngakube abawaboni yini amakameli ukuthi adalwa kanjani na
  88,18,Nesibhakabhaka ukuthi saphakanyiswa kanjani
  88,19,Nezintaba ukuthi zakhiwa kanjani
  88,20,Nomhlaba ukuthi wendlalwa kanjani
  88,21,"Ngakho-ke khumbuza, kuphela wena ungumkhumbuzi"
  88,22,Awusiyena umphoqi kubona ukuthi bakholwe
  88,23,Ngaphandle kwalowo ofulathelayo futhi angakholwa
  88,24,Ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi uyomjezisa ngesijeziso esikhulu kakhulu
  88,25,Ngempela kukuthina ukuphindela kwabo
  88,26,Bese ngempela kuba kuthina ukubalelwa kwabo
  89,1,Ngifunga ngokusa
  89,2,Futhi ngifunga nangobusuku obuyishumi
  89,3,Futhi ngifunga nangokulingene nokukodwa (okungalingani)
  89,4,Futhi ngifunga nangobusuku ngenkathi buhamba
  89,5,Ngakube kulokho kunesifundo kulowo oqondayo
  89,6,Awuzange yini ubone ukuthi yenza kanjani iNkosi yakho ku- Ad
  89,7,I – iram enezinsika (eziqatha eziphakeme)
  89,8,Okuyiyona okungekho okwakhiwe njengayo ezweni
  89,9,Kanye noThamud okunguyena owagumba idwala esigodini
  89,10,NoFaro umnikazi wezigxobo
  89,11,Labo abangazange bahloniphe ezweni
  89,12,(uFaro nabantu bakhe) benza okuningi ukukhwabanisa kulona (izwe)
  89,13,Ngakho-ke iNkosi yakho yathela phezulu kwabo isijeziso
  89,14,Ngempela iNkosi yakho ingeqaphile
  89,15,"Mayelana nomuntu uma imlinga iNkosi yakhe bese imnika ukuhlonipheka bese imupha (umusa nokunye) bese ethi, “iNkosi yami iyangithanda”"
  89,16,"Kepha uma (iNkosi yakhe) imlinga ngokumncisha (noma imnciphisele) isabelo sakhe bese ethi, “iNkosi yami ingidumazile”"
  89,17,Lutho! Kepha aniyihloniphi intandane
  89,18,Futhi anibancengi abantu ukuthi bondle abampofu
  89,19,Futhi nidla ifa ngokudla komona
  89,20,Futhi nithanda ingcebo ngothando olukhulu
  89,21,Lutho! Futhi khumbula ngenkathi umhlaba ubuthuzeka wendlaleka ubayizicucu
  89,22,Futhi khumbula ngenkathi iNkosi yakho iza kanye nezingelosi zingolayini (ngezigaba zazo)
  89,23,"Futhi isihogo ngalolosuku siyokwenziwa ukuthi sibeseduzane, ngalolosuku umuntu uyokhumbula, futhi ukukhumbula kwakhe kuyomsiza ngani na"
  89,24,"Uyothi, “Oh ukuba nje ngangithumele ngaphambili (okuhle) kwempilo yami"
  89,25,"Ngakho-ke\tngalolosuku\takekho\tongajezisa\tngendlela (uMvelinqangi) azojezisa ngayo"
  89,26,Futhi akekho ongabopha ngendlela ayobopha ngayo
  89,27,Oh mphefumulo onokuthula
  89,28,Phindela eNkosini yakho uthokozile uthokozisa
  89,29,Ngakho-ke ngena phakathi kwezinceku zami
  89,30,Futhi ungene (esivandeni) ezulwini lami